[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to the world\'s first-ever AI assistant for interface design Motiff AI 2.0 Let\'s meet your AI design partner right now You can summon Motiff AI anytime in the right sidebar By clicking or box selecting'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the context is easily shared with Motiff AI Simply select a frame that you want to edit in the design and Motiff AI will quickly provide you with some new options'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
